 <div class="manual-notes" id="user-notes">
  <h3>User Notes:</h3>
<div class="note">
 <div class="note_handle">Note by: <a href="/user/doconnor">doconnor</a></div>
 <div class="note_time"><a name="13455"></a><a href="#13455">2010-11-08 09:43 UTC</a></div>
 <div class="note_text">
  Windows users should take a look at http://pear.php.net/manual/en/installation.getting.php<br />
<br />
Effectively, you simply Start Menu -&gt; Run -&gt; CMD<br />
<br />
c:\cd php<br />
c:\php\go-pear.bat<br />
<br />
The other instructions are really only suited for manual installation, and I would never, ever recommend them. </div>
</div>
<div class="note">
 <div class="note_handle">Note by: &#x75;&#115;&#x65;&#114;&#x40;&#101;&#x78;&#97;&#x6d;&#112;&#x6c;&#101;&#x2e;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;</div>
